9th Field Arty Reg Flash.svg|<center>82nd ABN DIV ARTY's 319th Field Artillery Regiment, [[3rd Battalion, 319th Field Artillery Regiment|3rd Battalion]]</center>\nFile:US Army 4th BN-319th Field Arty Reg Flash.svg|<center>[[173rd Airborne Brigade Combat Team|173rd Airborne Brigade's]] 319th Field Artillery Regiment, [[4th Battalion, 319th Field Artillery Regiment|4th Battalion]]</center>\n</gallery>\n\n====[[Infantry Branch (United States)|Infantry]]====\n<gallery>\nFile:75thrangerflash.svg|<center>[[United States Army Special Operations Command|US Army Special Operations Command]]'s (USASOC) [[75th Ranger Regiment (United States)|75th Ranger Regiment]] and [[Special Troops Battalion]]</center>\nFile:1 Bn 75 Ranger Regiment Beret Flash.svg|<center>USASOC's [[1st Ranger Battalion (United States)|75th Ranger Regiment, 1st Battalion]]</center>\nFile:Image5435.gif|<center>USASOC's [[2nd Ranger Battalion (United States)|75th Ranger Regiment, 2nd Battalion]]</center>\nFile:Image5436.gif|<center>USASOC's [[3rd Ranger Battalion (United States)|75th Ranger Regiment, 3rd Battalion]]</center>\nFile:US Army 4th Bde-25th ID Flash.png|<center>[[25th Infantry Division (United States)|25th Infantry (INF) Division's (DIV)]], [[4th Brigade Combat Team (Airborne), 25th Infantry Division|4th Infantry Brigade Combat Team]] (IBCT)</center>\nFile:US Army 1st Bn-501st Inf Reg Flash.svg|<center>25th INF DIV, 4th IBCT's [[501st Infantry Regiment (United States)|501st Infantry Regiment]], 1st Battalion</center>\nFile:US Army 3rd Bn-509th Inf Reg Flash.png|<center>25th INF DIV, 4th IBCT's [[509th Infantry Regiment (United States)|509th Infantry Regiment]], 3rd Battalion</center>\nFile:US Army 82nd ABN DIV Flash.png|<center>[[82nd Airborne Division|82nd Airborne (ABN) DIV]]</center>\nFile:504th Infantry Regiment Beret Flash.svg|<center>82nd ABN DIV's 1st IBCT</center>\nFile:US Army 2nd BN-501st PIR Flash.png|<center>82nd ABN DIV, 1st IBCT's 501st Infantry Regiment, 2nd Battalion</center>\nFile:504InfRegt1BnFlash.PNG|<center>82nd ABN DIV, 1st IBCT's [[504th Infantry Regiment (United States)|504th Infantry Regiment]], 1st Battalion</center>\nFile:504InfRegt2BnFlash.png|<center>82nd ABN DIV, 1st IBCT's 504th Infantry Regiment, 2nd Battalion</center>\nFile:US Army-82nd Airborne Division-2nd Brigade Combat Team-Beret Flash.svg|<center>82nd ABN DIV's 2nd IBCT</center>\nFile:US Army 1st BN-325th Inf Reg Flash.svg|<center>82nd ABN DIV, 2nd IBCT's [[325th Infantry Regiment (United States)|325th Infantry Regiment]], 1st Battalion</center>\nFile:US Army 2nd BN-325th Inf Reg Flash.svg|<center>82nd ABN DIV, 2nd IBCT's 325th Infantry Regiment, 2nd Battalion</center>\nFile:US Army 2nd BN-508th PIR Flash.png|<center>82nd ABN DIV, 2nd IBCT's [[508th Infantry Regiment (United States)|508th Infantry Regiment]], 2nd Battalion</center>\nFile:US Army-82nd Airborne Division-3rd Brigade Combat Team-Beret Flash.svg|<center>82nd ABN DIV's 3rd IBCT</center>\nFile:US Army 1st BN-505th Inf Reg Flash.svg|<center>82nd ABN DIV, 3rd IBCT's [[505th Infantry Regiment (United States)|505th Infantry Regiment]], 1st Battalion</center>\nFile:US Army 2nd BN-505th Inf Reg Flash.svg|<center>82nd ABN DIV, 3rd IBCT's 505th Infantry Regiment, 2nd Battalion</center>\nFile:US Army 1st BN-508th PIR Flash.png|<center>82nd ABN DIV, 3rd IBCT's 508th Infantry Regiment, 1st Battalion</center>\nFile:US Army 173rd ABN INF BCT Flash.png|<center>[[173rd Airborne Brigade Combat Team|173rd Airborne Brigade]]</center>\nFile:US Army 143rd ABN INF BN Flash.png|<center>173rd Airborne Brigade's [[143rd Infantry Regiment (United States)|143rd Infantry Regiment]], 1st Battalion</center>\nFile:US Army 1st BN-503rd Inf Reg Flash.svg|<center>173rd Airborne Brigade's [[503rd Infantry Regiment (United States)|503rd Infantry Regiment]], 1st Battalion</center>\nFile:US Army 2nd BN-503rd Inf Reg Flash.svg|<center>173rd Airborne Brigade's 503rd Infantry Regiment, 2nd Battalion</center>\n</gallery>\n\n====[[Military Intelligence 